{"text_id":140971,"tokens":["There"," are"," valid"," arguments"," for"," and"," against"," both"," teacher","-","designed"," and"," student","-","created"," summer"," assignments","."," On"," the"," one"," hand",","," assigning"," summer"," projects"," created"," by"," teachers"," ensures"," curriculum"," alignment"," and"," guarantees"," a"," level"," of"," academic"," rigor"," that"," might"," otherwise"," be"," lacking"," if"," students"," were"," to"," design"," their"," own"," assignments","."," This"," can"," help"," ensure"," that"," students"," are"," consistently"," challenged"," throughout"," their"," academic"," careers",","," maintaining"," steady"," academic"," engagement",","," and"," preventing"," summer"," learning"," loss","."," ","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," assigning"," student","-","created"," summer"," projects"," may"," encourage"," higher"," levels"," of"," investment"," and"," interest"," from"," students","."," This"," approach"," allows"," students"," to"," have"," agency"," and"," choice"," in"," their"," learning",","," which"," can"," foster"," a"," sense"," of"," ownership"," and"," motivation"," to"," learn","."," Additionally",","," this"," can"," help"," students"," develop"," valuable"," self","-","directed"," learning"," skills"," that"," can"," benefit"," them"," in"," their"," present"," and"," future"," education"," and"," beyond","."," ","\n\n","However",","," there"," is"," also"," a"," risk"," that"," some"," students"," may"," choose"," to"," create"," projects"," that"," do"," not"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum"," or"," put"," in"," minimal"," effort",","," which"," could"," result"," in"," an"," uneven"," playing"," field"," among"," students","."," To"," mitigate"," this",","," teachers"," can"," provide"," students"," with"," choice"," boards"," or"," playlists"," that"," outline"," acceptable"," topics"," and"," resources"," to"," guide"," their"," project"," ideas"," and"," ensure"," a"," minimum"," level"," of"," effort"," is"," achieved","."," Additionally",","," teachers"," can"," require"," students"," to"," submit"," a"," proposal"," for"," their"," project"," to"," ensure"," it"," aligns"," with"," the"," curriculum","."," ","\n\n","To"," address"," the"," concern"," of"," teacher"," workload"," in"," designing"," summer"," assignments",","," schools"," could"," consider"," hiring"," summer"," curriculum"," designers"," who"," would"," be"," specialized"," in"," creating"," engaging"," and"," curriculum","-","aligned"," projects"," for"," students","."," This"," would"," relieve"," the"," burden"," on"," teachers"," while"," potentially"," improving"," the"," quality"," of"," summer"," assignments","."," ","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," a"," balanced"," approach"," that"," incorporates"," elements"," of"," both"," teacher","-","designed"," and"," student","-","created"," summer"," assignments"," appears"," to"," be"," the"," most"," effective","."," This"," approach"," allows"," for"," the"," benefits"," of"," curriculum"," alignment"," and"," academic"," challenge"," while"," also"," providing"," students"," with"," opportunities"," for"," self","-","directed"," learning"," and"," engagement","."," To"," achieve"," this"," effectively",","," teachers"," should"," be"," provided"," with"," training"," and"," support"," to"," develop"," high","-","quality",","," flexible"," assignments"," that"," can"," be"," adapted"," to"," student"," needs"," and"," interests","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," expand"," on"," any"," of"," the"," points"," in"," this"," essay","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}